00:00:37.090 --> 00:00:41.030
When I was a child
I was fascinated
by the spontaneity

00:00:41.030 --> 00:00:43.600
and the freedom of the clown.

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:48.100
[♪ music ♪]

00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:50.100
[♪ music ♪]

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:53.200
For me, the clown,
it was a whole human being

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:59.200
in the sense of humility,
of freedom, of dignity,
and the playfulness, yes.

00:00:59.930 --> 00:01:04.930
[♪ music ♪]

00:01:04.930 --> 00:01:10.350
[♪ music ♪]

00:01:10.350 --> 00:01:13.970
